Unfortunately, only Japanese version available at the moment as this game needs a voice actor. Planning to develop English version when I find a English voice actor. Play at : https://unityroom.com/games/yabacome

Relationship of elements, installs and rating in a game

components in a application game such as attached mini games and long story modes are huge element which form a game. From this fact, I formed a hypothesis. More elements in a game the better. This simply means that if the game has long story and more components to it, the game will get better reviews and installs compared to a small game. I have analysed one of open dataset to investigate the correlation of size of a game and ratings, installs. details : https://github.com/Saku052/GooglePlayAnalysis/blob/main/PlayWeightAnalysis.ipynb

Android app - My Z score

Instead of comparing yourself with others, why don't you just compare with past self. When you just cant stop comparing yourself with others simply install this app and force yourself to look at your past score and check out your Z score. Install at : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Saku.watashinohensachi

Android game - Break out

Breakout game with weapons which increases your score. acquire a weapon each time you complete new level. Obtain all weapons by completing all levels. Install at : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Saku.ComboBlock
